item.title: About SD Transfer
item.description: Note The SD transfer is current supported on these configurations: MK WiFi modules using MKS Serial Protocol (~110KB/s) MKS Robin MKS TFT Using some sharing solution like : Panucatt WiFi Backpack Panucatt Azteeg X5 ESP3D wireless module Using a direct connection to SD but content is only accessible by ESP and not usable by connected system, like: on ESPCam32
